Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.90,0:22:12.91,ED Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\blur5}atarimae no you ni sugite iku
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.91,0:22:19.25,ED Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\blur5}nanige nai shiawase mitsukete wa
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.25,0:22:24.88,ED Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\blur5}toikakete kurukawaita kaze ni
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.88,0:22:30.40,ED Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\blur5}fuwari mau hana hitohira
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.28,0:22:42.77,ED Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\blur5}itsuka itsuka to himeru awaku senmei na kage
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.77,0:22:49.32,ED Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\blur5}mada koko de iki wo surukarenu itami to
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.32,0:22:58.56,ED Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\blur5}anata wo matsu sore dake
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.01,0:23:17.21,ED Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\blur5}nanige nai shiawase ikiru kono sekai de
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.90,0:22:12.91,ED Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}Tudo se foi tão naturalmente,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.91,0:22:19.25,ED Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}buscando uma simples felicidade.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.25,0:22:24.88,ED Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}No vento seco que me desafia,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.88,0:22:30.40,ED Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}uma única flor voando.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.28,0:22:42.77,ED Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}Um dia, em algum lugar, a sombra tênue e radiante se esconderá.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.77,0:22:49.32,ED Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}Ainda estou aqui e respirando, aguentando essa dor,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.32,0:22:58.56,ED Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}apenas esperando por você.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.01,0:23:17.21,ED Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}Encontrando uma simples felicidade neste mundo em que vivo.
